  {
    "id": "1813195618258460906",
    "text": "JD Vance wrote Hillbilly Elegy in 2016. \n\nHillbilly Elegy went on to become a movie in 2020.\n\nHillybilly Elegy is the memoir of JD Vance before his political career started.\n\nJD Vance went from having nothing to be  being the nominee for Vice President.\n\n https://t.co/txv2EoDPpM",
