  {
    "id": "1813051726854766907",
    "text": "Something irksome about \"Hillbilly Elegy\" discourse is the frequent misapprehension that it's about Vance growing up in \"Appalachia.\" As the book makes clear, it's about his growing up in the steel town of Middletown OH (green) w/ family that migrated from Eastern KY (yellow) 1/2 https://t.co/9bgBniSF8I",
    "author": {
      "id": "436925910",
      "name": "Alec MacGillis",
      "screenName": "AlecMacGillis",
      "profileImageUrl": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1864477731544612864/EFFem_dz_normal.jpg",
      "verified": true
    },
    "metrics": {
      "likes": 677,
